text: Louise Lenormand (born 1901, date of death unknown) was a French diver. She competed in the women's 3 metre springboard event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:Year of death missing Category:French female divers Category:Olympic divers of France Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
